CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 17, 1956, pg. B11, reads: "'Here Let Me Show You' says Atty. Leroy Irvis, second from left, as he shows one of his 'Bird Boys' what to do with a model plane. - Harris Photo."Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 17, 1956, pg. B11, reads: "'Bird Boys' of Pittsburgh getting their planes ready to wheel are, left to right, Jackie Butler, LuGene Bray, Milton Swan Jr., Sam Anderson and Leroy Randall Jr. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Leroy Randall Jr., K. Leroy Irvis, LuGene "Buddy" Bray, John "Jackie" Gordon Butler, Milton Swan Jr., and Sam Anderson seated in front, with radio-controlled model airplanes in Irvis' workshop
